summary: MCU CosmicCast Episode 31 Loki Series Confirmed and Joe Russo's Avengers Q&A
title: MCU CosmicCast Episode 31 Loki Series Confirmed and Joe Russo's Avengers Q&A
body:
MCU CosmicCast Episode 31 Loki Series Confirmed and Joe Russo’s Avengers Q&A

Welcome to episode 31 of the MCU ComsicCast, capping off a pretty eventful week for MCU news!

On this week’s episode:

  • The Loki series on Disney+ is officially confirmed with Tom Hiddleston returning.
  • Captain Marvel is confirmed to be set in 1995.
  • Joe Russo does an Avengers 4 Q&A with some big news coming from it.
  • That Black Widow plot synopsis that was going around is proven to be fake.
  • Sebastian…

title: #4: This Female Fights Back
body:
We finally get to read a comic where Carol is the star! In this episode, we cover the 1977 Ms. Marvel #1. Topics include: Carol as a liberated woman, Carol having a suspicious amount in common with Spider-Man, mysterious hairstyles, J. K. Simmons is the greatest, and some talk about Mary Sues.


Check out this episode!
